{"tid":2032974,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"尖東忌廉哥離世　粉絲排隊瞻仰遺容痛哭","createTime":"2020-05-24T11:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T14:42:35.000Z","uid":104138,"like":32,"dislike":743,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"7e0e95dc0909266467cb8fce6043ba9fc55150e7","tid":2032974,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"香港最紅貓店長的「尖東忌廉哥」，2012年因一次走失事件而紅遍中外，惟今日不敵病魔，主人高先生在Facebook專頁宣布忌廉哥死訊，指粉絲可以到油麻地店舖見貓貓最後一面。今午4時，約30名粉絲到場送別忌廉哥，部分人見到忌廉哥的遺容時即眼眶泛紅，撫摸其遺體時傷心落淚。<br />\n<br />\n高先生表示，忌廉哥患胃癌多月，今日在妻子懷抱中安詳離世。雖然愛貓已去了「彩虹橋」，但高先生希望忌廉哥精神遺留在人間，令大眾繼續愛惜動物，亦希望忌廉哥的基金能延續，幫助更多動物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4546408/org/c34d51445b05e6ef6a969949f6dd8f7e.jpg/c8ikAN1Ih5xdgtaJgcq3rA55OBECRiyCG49a-zGPWvs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4546408%2Forg%2Fc34d51445b05e6ef6a969949f6dd8f7e.jpg%2Fc8ikAN1Ih5xdgtaJgcq3rA55OBECRiyCG49a-zGPWvs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8d8d8679&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4210ecd2fb597c4690c0862a350d68b27826711d","tid":2032974,"uid":41116,"like":384,"dislike":14,"score":370,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:04:17.000Z","msg":"無得再消費佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea26ab125e23f1c173cb047f010da9629c0e9a4","tid":2032974,"uid":3063,"like":415,"dislike":8,"score":407,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"但高先生希望忌廉哥精神遺留在人間<br />\n<br />\n？？<br />\n精神領袖<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野精神<br />\n養貓賺錢？"},{"pid":"8c81f3d4ad45b1ea19208e8f8f26445be67d0233","tid":2032974,"uid":104138,"like":69,"dislike":5,"score":64,"quote":{"pid":"eea26ab125e23f1c173cb047f010da9629c0e9a4","tid":2032974,"uid":3063,"like":415,"dislike":8,"score":407,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"但高先生希望忌廉哥精神遺留在人間<br />\n<br />\n？？<br />\n精神領袖<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野精神<br />\n養貓賺錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"代表一國兩制已死既精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=